* Tallys how many T-shirts of each size
* Quickly Calculates Totals for Logistics and Inventory
* When to use:      Use this for pre-race or post-race logistics, such as counting how many T-shirts to order, medals needed, or the gender breakdown of the field.
* How to use:       Use the BY command on a field (like TSHIRT) without listing any other Field commands. This tells RunScore to simply count the occurrences rather than listing every runner.
* Pro Tip:          Use BY PERCENT if you need to see the mathematical breakdown (e.g., "Large = 10 (21.3%)") for easier ordering.
no page numbers
BY                  TSHIRT
